  <description type="morphology">Stem segments broadly obovate to subcircular, 15–30 × 12.5–25 cm, sometimes broader than wide, to 1.5 times longer than wide. Spines (0–)1–6 per areole, evenly distributed on stem segment to absent, yellow throughout, sometimes with red or red-brown extreme bases, aging blackish, longest 12–75 mm. 2n = 66.</description>
